### TuVi backend — REST Client (VS Code / IntelliJ)
@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 1) Health
GET {{base}}/health

### 2) Solar hợp lệ → 200
POST {{base}}/generate-reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "birth_day": 15,
  "birth_month": 1,
  "birth_year": 1995,
  "birth_hour": 16,
  "birth_minute": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "calendar_type": "solar",
  "is_leap_lunar_month": false
}

### 3) Solar + leap=true → 200, normalize leap=false, log solar_calendar_leap_flag_overridden_to_false
POST {{base}}/generate-reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "birth_day": 15,
  "birth_month": 1,
  "birth_year": 1995,
  "birth_hour": 16,
  "birth_minute": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "calendar_type": "solar",
  "is_leap_lunar_month": true
}

### 4) Lunar thiếu leap → 422 MISSING_IS_LEAP_LUNAR_MONTH
POST {{base}}/generate-reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "birth_day": 15,
  "birth_month": 1,
  "birth_year": 1995,
  "birth_hour": 16,
  "birth_minute": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "calendar_type": "lunar"
}

### 5) OpenAI: unset OPENAI_API_KEY hoặc key sai → 200, teaser = mock, log openai_teaser_fallback_mock
# (Chạy server không set OPENAI_API_KEY hoặc key không hợp lệ)
POST {{base}}/generate-reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "birth_day": 15,
  "birth_month": 1,
  "birth_year": 1995,
  "birth_hour": 16,
  "birth_minute": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "calendar_type": "solar",
  "is_leap_lunar_month": false
}

### 6) Messenger webhook verify (token đúng)
GET {{base}}/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=test_verify_token&hub.challenge=12345

### 7) Messenger webhook text event sample
POST {{base}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "object": "page",
  "entry": [
    {
      "id": "PAGE_ID",
      "time": 1710000000,
      "messaging": [
        {
          "sender": { "id": "USER_123" },
          "recipient": { "id": "PAGE_ID" },
          "timestamp": 1710000001,
          "message": {
            "mid": "m_1",
            "text": "start"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 8) Messenger webhook non-text sample
POST {{base}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "object": "page",
  "entry": [
    {
      "id": "PAGE_ID",
      "time": 1710000000,
      "messaging": [
        {
          "sender": { "id": "USER_456" },
          "recipient": { "id": "PAGE_ID" },
          "timestamp": 1710000001,
          "message": {
            "mid": "m_2",
            "attachments": [
              { "type": "image", "payload": { "url": "https://example.com/a.jpg" } }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
